<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0071001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0071001">原語 lañja = lañca Davida &amp; Stede 之波利字書及 Mahāvastu 見索引。</note>
<note n="0072002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072002">本文 byākataṁ c'asi nāgassa 是 byākato c'asi nāgassa？</note>
<note n="0072003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072003">本文 patiṭṭhissami 是 patiṭṭhapessāmi？</note>
<note n="0072004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072004">本文 gamanaṁ 是 gammaṁ（gamy aṁ）或 gamikaṁ, gamiyaṁ？</note>
<note n="0072005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072005">本文 anupavattissati 是 anuppavattessati？</note>
<note n="0073006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073006">本文 thale 採用脚注異本之 phale。</note>
<note n="0073007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073007"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0073008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073008">原語 ṁuñja 屬甘蔗之一種 babbaja 是雜草之一種。</note>
<note n="0073009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073009">本文 kilesakalabhūta 是 kilesasakalābhibhūta？</note>
<note n="0073010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073010">本文為 ālokaṁ dassayissāmi, jotayissāmi kevalaṁ Tambapaṇṇim janasānan ti alokaṁ dassayissāmi kevalaṁ Tumbapaṇṇim jotayissāmi jinasāsana ti？</note>
<note n="0073011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073011"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0073012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073012">本文 tesaṁ santapaiyissāma 是 tesam pakāsayissāma？</note>
<note n="0074013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0074013">眉沙迦（Missaka）Anurādhapura 之東，今之 Mihitale Mitton. The Lost cities of Ceylon（p. 53）由市鎮（Anurādhapura）有八哩。</note>
<note n="0074014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0074014">本文 uppatito thero 是 uppatitā therā？</note>
<note n="0074015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0074015">本文 patiṭṭhito 是 patiṭṭhita？</note>
<note n="0075016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075016">本文 addasam 是 addassa？</note>
<note n="0075017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075017">本文 manussa lokeyaṁ 是 lokiyaṁ？</note>
<note n="0075018" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075018">本文 ca pāvisi 是 upavisi？</note>
<note n="0075019" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075019">在大王統史有小象跡喻經（Cūlahatthipadūpama suttanta）。（大王統史第十四章二二）</note>
<note n="0075020" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0075020">本文 gacchasi 是 gaccāhi？</note>
<note n="0076021" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076021">依大王統史有命令馭者於翌朝連行長老於街市。</note>
<note n="0076022" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076022">本文 tathāgataṁ 是 tathāgate？</note>
<note n="0076023" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076023">本文 thero vasi mahiddhiko 是 therā v mahiddhikā？</note>
<note n="0076024" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076024">本文 orahetvā 是 orhitvāna？</note>
<note n="0076025" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076025">本文 parupite 是 pārupante？</note>
<note n="0076026" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076026">本文 alaṁkatamaṇḍapā setā 是 maṇḍapaṁ selaṁ maṁ？</note>
<note n="0076027" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0076027">本文 ayaṁ acchariyaṁ 是 aho acchariyaṁ？</note>
<note n="0077028" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0077028">本文 pavisetvāna 是 pavisitvāna。</note>
<note n="0077029" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0077029">本文 dussavārite 是 dussacchādite？</note>
<note n="0077030" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0077030">本文 Samantap p. 80 參照。本文 rañño sahattā 是 rājā sahattā？</note>
<note n="0077031" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0077031">本文 āvatā 是 āvaṭā？</note>
<note n="0077032" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0077032">本文 tesaṁ 是 tāsaṁ？</note>
<note n="0077033" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0077033">本文 saddhājātā vibuddhimā 是 saddhājato buddhimā（V. 58 參照）。</note>
<note n="0077034" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0077034">見 Samanta p. 80。</note>
</p>
